name: 1971 Morris Oxford Series VI
description: Over the course of the last 8 years, my father and four generations of my family worked on a 1971 Morris Oxford Series VI it was a true labour of love. The car will be going back to auction soon and I just wanted to create a piece as a way to archive the experience. My grandfather passed away before seeing it completed and in some ways, it's a way to just record that it happened. A piece of family history.
